{"tid":2264182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺呢幾個月屌人打尖爽好多，啲人俾我屌到聲都唔敢出","createTime":"2020-10-30T12:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T08:21:47.000Z","uid":32645,"like":43,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b622658c48992bba5b8738b45fb659b056ea1e22","tid":2264182,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"日撚日返工搭小巴都有人打尖，最近一見到有廢老想打尖就即刻屌：<br />\n咪撚打尖呀屌你老母！識佢又點呀？黃絲大曬呀，死暴徒！唔係暴徒？咁你就守下規矩啦！<br />\n<br />\n見到有死𡃁仔打尖就屌佢：<br />\n排隊啦屌你老母，冇規冇矩，你去考警察啦柒頭！<br />\n<br />\n通常廢老都好厚面皮，會依依哦哦，但屌多佢兩句暴徒就會走，再唔走就話報警搵警察打柒佢就知驚，後生仔就一屌即走<br />\n以前都唔敢開聲屌，依家屌人都大聲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ac9b7fcb2986d739437ff6566f1949f15c1073","tid":2264182,"uid":67041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:28:25.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"98d9cf27aba75129017b8b126d42389285e3fe42","tid":2264182,"uid":254535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:31:07.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"a8f59b3963400eb435d28d20298cf92c256b5bba","tid":2264182,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ea77602b98390c9fcc9599ff06d8cf273f60e3e","tid":2264182,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8f59b3963400eb435d28d20298cf92c256b5bba","tid":2264182,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"啱聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又多個詞彙用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be052217872fd7c7959081a3fd10351bb687851","tid":2264182,"uid":54975,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"真實情況係樓豬畀人打尖，聲都唔敢聲。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好嬲好嬲，跟住心入邊屌人老母。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}